# Research Assistant — REST Client (VS Code: REST Client by Huachao Mao)
# Run worker: npm run worker:research-assistant (from repo root)

@base = http://localhost:3000
@workflowId = <paste workflowId from start response>

### Start content-brief workflow
POST {{base}}/workflows/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workflowType": "contentBrief",
  "input": {
    "topic": "Sustainable packaging in e-commerce",
    "audience": "B2B"
  }
}

### Start research assistant agent
POST {{base}}/agents/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agentName": "researchAssistant",
  "input": {
    "message": "What is the latest news on the war in Iran?"
  }
}

### Get run status
GET {{base}}/runs/{{workflowId}}

### Get run result (wait until status is COMPLETED)
GET {{base}}/runs/{{workflowId}}/result
